unipager (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Implements statistics HTTP API endpoint at /status
  * Implements password authentication for webinterface and websocket
  * Adds message type und function bit options for test messages
  * Adds experimental support for Raspager 2
  * Fixes several bugs

